  "label": "Conflict between different principles (Autonomy vs. Beneficence)",
  "explanation": "There is a prima facie obligation to respect the father’s decision and a prima facie obligation to benefit the child. In this case, promoting the child’s wellbeing takes priority over honoring the parental choice."
